19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_minfo(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24 int i;
25 bool ok;
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
28
29 UNUSED(type);
30 UNUSED(rdclass);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 if (origin == NULL)
34 origin = dns_rootname;
35
36 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
37 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
38 isc_tokentype_string,
39 false));
40 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
41 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
42 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin,
43 options, target));
44 ok = true;
45 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0)
46 ok = dns_name_ismailbox(&name);
47 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
48 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
49 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
50 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
51 }
52 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
53}
54
55static inline isc_result_t
56totext_minfo(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
57 isc_region_t region;
58 dns_name_t rmail;
59 dns_name_t email;
60 dns_name_t prefix;
61 bool sub;
62
63 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
64 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
65
66 dns_name_init(&rmail, NULL);
67 dns_name_init(&email, NULL);
68 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
69
70 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
71
72 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
73 isc_region_consume(&region, rmail.length);
74
75 dns_name_fromregion(&email, &region);
76 isc_region_consume(&region, email.length);
77
78 sub = name_prefix(&rmail, tctx->origin, &prefix);
79
80 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
81
82 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
83
84 sub = name_prefix(&email, tctx->origin, &prefix);
85 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
86}
87
88static inline isc_result_t
89fromwire_minfo(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
90 dns_name_t rmail;
91 dns_name_t email;
92
93 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
94
95 UNUSED(type);
96 UNUSED(rdclass);
97
98 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
99
100 dns_name_init(&rmail, NULL);
101 dns_name_init(&email, NULL);
102
103 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&rmail, source, dctx, options, target));
104 return (dns_name_fromwire(&email, source, dctx, options, target));
105}
106
107static inline isc_result_t
108towire_minfo(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
109 isc_region_t region;
110 dns_name_t rmail;
111 dns_name_t email;
112 dns_offsets_t roffsets;
113 dns_offsets_t eoffsets;
114
115 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
116 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
117
118 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
119
120 dns_name_init(&rmail, roffsets);
121 dns_name_init(&email, eoffsets);
122
123 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
124
125 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
126 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&rmail));
127
128 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&rmail, cctx, target));
129
130 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
131 isc_region_consume(&region, rmail.length);
132
133 return (dns_name_towire(&rmail, cctx, target));
134}

136static inline int
137compare_minfo(ARGS_COMPARE) {
138 isc_region_t region1;
139 isc_region_t region2;
140 dns_name_t name1;
141 dns_name_t name2;
142 int order;
143
144 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
145 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
146 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
147 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
148 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
149
150 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
151 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
152
153 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
154 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
155
156 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
157 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
158
159 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
160 if (order != 0)
161 return (order);
162
163 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
164 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
165
166 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
167 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
168
169 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
170 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
171
172 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
173 return (order);
174}

176static inline isc_result_t
177fromstruct_minfo(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
178 dns_rdata_minfo_t *minfo = source;
179 isc_region_t region;
180
181 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
182 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
183 REQUIRE(minfo->common.rdtype == type);
184 REQUIRE(minfo->common.rdclass == rdclass);
185
186 UNUSED(type);
187 UNUSED(rdclass);
188
189 dns_name_toregion(&minfo->rmailbox, &region);
190 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
191 dns_name_toregion(&minfo->emailbox, &region);
192 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
193}
194
195static inline isc_result_t
196tostruct_minfo(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
197 dns_rdata_minfo_t *minfo = target;
198 isc_region_t region;
199 dns_name_t name;
200 isc_result_t result;
201
202 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
203 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
204 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
205
206 minfo->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
207 minfo->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
208 ISC_LINK_INIT(&minfo->common, link);
209
210 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
211 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
212 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
213 dns_name_init(&minfo->rmailbox, NULL);
214 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &minfo->rmailbox));
215 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
216
217 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
218 dns_name_init(&minfo->emailbox, NULL);
219 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &minfo->emailbox);
220 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
221 goto cleanup;
222 minfo->mctx = mctx;
223 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
224
225 cleanup:
226 if (mctx != NULL)
227 dns_name_free(&minfo->rmailbox, mctx);
228 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
229}
230
231static inline void
232freestruct_minfo(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
233 dns_rdata_minfo_t *minfo = source;
234
235 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
236 REQUIRE(minfo->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
237
238 if (minfo->mctx == NULL)
239 return;
240
241 dns_name_free(&minfo->rmailbox, minfo->mctx);
242 dns_name_free(&minfo->emailbox, minfo->mctx);
243 minfo->mctx = NULL;
244}

246static inline isc_result_t
247additionaldata_minfo(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
248 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
249
250 UNUSED(rdata);
251 UNUSED(add);
252 UNUSED(arg);
253
254 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
255}

257static inline isc_result_t
258digest_minfo(ARGS_DIGEST) {
259 isc_region_t r;
260 dns_name_t name;
261 isc_result_t result;
262
263 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
264
265 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
266 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
267 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
268 result = dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg);
269 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
270 return (result);
271 isc_region_consume(&r, name_length(&name));
272 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
273 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
274
275 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
276}

278static inline bool
279checkowner_minfo(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
280
281 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
282
283 UNUSED(name);
284 UNUSED(type);
285 UNUSED(rdclass);
286 UNUSED(wildcard);
287
288 return (true);
289}
290
291static inline bool
292checknames_minfo(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
293 isc_region_t region;
294 dns_name_t name;
295
296 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_minfo);
297
298 UNUSED(owner);
299
300 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
301 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
302 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
303 if (!dns_name_ismailbox(&name)) {
304 if (bad != NULL)
305 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
306 return (false);
307 }
308 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
309 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
310 if (!dns_name_ismailbox(&name)) {
311 if (bad != NULL)
312 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
313 return (false);
314 }
315 return (true);
316}
317
318static inline int
319casecompare_minfo(ARGS_COMPARE) {
320 return (compare_minfo(rdata1, rdata2));
321}
